com.vernalis.knime.mmp

Class FragmentValue2

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vernalis.knime.mmp.FragmentValue2
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<FragmentValue2>

    public class FragmentValue2
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<FragmentValue2>
    Simple container class to hold an ID string and SMILES String together and allow comparison and sorting for use in HashSet etc
    Author:
    s.roughley <knime@vernalis.com>
